question: How should one proceed to stop spreading the fertilizer?
model_answer:
To stop spreading the fertilizer:
1. Close all the doors and windows in the cabin.
2. Switch on the control box.
3. Check the settings as described in the instructions.
4. Start driving and open the dosing units at the same time by pressing the start key.
5. The rpm of the tractor engine (therefore also of the PTO shaft) must remain constant while spreading.
6. Drive to the next tramline and re-start the spreader at the right time, as displayed in the instructions.
7. In the event of spreader failure or stoppage: Stop spreading immediately! Disconnect the PTO shaft immediately!
